Class OrderFinishedEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • org.springframework.context.ApplicationEvent
        • workshop.applicationEvents.OrderFinishedEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class OrderFinishedEvent
extends org.springframework.context.ApplicationEvent
    Special class only for particular type of ApplicationEvent which invokes in Order.preUpdate() when all Order's Task's are set to Task#getFinished() or the Order itself is set to 'finished' state.
